Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:12.11,Italics Dialogue,Alarm,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, sleepyhead! Time to—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:17.27,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.45,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,Taroumaru, breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:52.46,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,Taroumaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.61,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,Taroumaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:05.11,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.25,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.52,Main Dialogue,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
